15 year ending June 30, 2026, the sum of One Hundred Fifty Thousand
16 Dollars ($150,000.00) or so much thereof as may be necessary for the
17 purpose of entering into a contract with a 501(c)(3) nonprofit
18 organization headquartered in Oklahoma, that specializes in
19 geography instruction and training of educators, to increase
20 geographic literacy in Oklahoma schools.
21 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective July 1, 2025.
